Loved the ravioli, stewed pork cheeks and prosciutto with melon. Their signature wine in bowl is excellent too! Highly recommend.

tip.text: The mains are limited, but good. Had the beef and fish. Coffee is great too. Special mention of the service: friendly, prompt and warm. Hope they keep the quality of the food and service consistent!
